quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,29,"aur ae baradran qoum, mein iss kaam par tum se koi maal nahi mangta, mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur mein unn logon ko dhakkay dainay se bhi raha jinhon ne meri baat maani hai, woh aap hi apne rab ke huzoor jaane walay hain magar mein daikhta hon ke tum log jahalat bart rahay ho"
11,30,"aur ae qoum, agar mein inn logon ko dhtkar dun to khuda ki pakar se kon mujhe bachanay aeye ga? tum logon ki samajh mein kya itni baat bhi nahi aati ?"
11,31,"aur mein tum se nahi kehta ke mere paas Allah ke khazanay hain, nah yeh kehta hon ke mein ghaib ka ilm rakhta hon, nah yeh mera daawa hai ke mein farishta hon aur yeh bhi mein nahi keh sakta ke jin logon ko tumhari ankhen hiqarat se dekhatii hain inhen Allah ne koi bhalai nahi di un ke nafs ka haal Allah hi behtar jaanta hai agar mein aisa kahoon to zalim hon ga """
11,32,"aakhir-kaar un logon ne kaha ke"" ae Nooh, tum ne hum se jhagra kya aur bohat kar liya ab to bas woh azaab le aao jis ki tum hamein dhamki dete ho agar sachey ho """
11,33,"Nooh ne jawab diya"" woh to Allah hi laaye ga, agar chahay ga, aur tum itna bil bota nahi rakhtay ke usay rok do"
11,34,"ab agar mein tumhari kuch kher khawahi karna bhi chahoon to meri kher khawahi tumhe koi faida nahi day sakti jabkay Allah hi ne tumhe bhatka dainay ka iradah kar liya ho, wohi tumhara rab hai aur usi ki taraf tumhe palatna hai """
11,35,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kya yeh log kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne yeh sab kuch khud ghurr liya hai? un se kaho"" agar mein ne yeh khud ghara hai to mujh par apne jurm ki zimma daari hai, aur jo jurm tum kar rahay ho is ki zimma daari se mein buri hon """
11,36,"Nooh par wahi ki gayi ke tumhari qoum mein se jo log imaan laa chuke bas woh laa chuke, ab koi maan-ne wala nahi hai un ke krtoton par gham khana chhorro"
11,37,"aur hamari nigrani mein hamari wahi ke mutabiq aik kashti banani shuru kar do aur dekho, jin logon ne zulm kya hai unn ke haq mein mujh se koi sifarish nah karna, yeh saaray ke saaray ab doobnay walay hain"
